You used an older version of the DMP template. Please use the Flemish standard DMP template. You can find this template in www.dmponline.be, along with guidance on what information is needed, or on the FWO website: https://fwo.be/en/about-fwo/research-policy/data-management-plan-dmp/
There are some rather generic pieces of text in your DMP (e.g. in the documentation and the data sharing section). Please make these more specific for this C3 project.
Please upload your updated DMP using the Flemish standard DMP template as intermediate.
